Class UnbindOperationWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.core.OperationWrapper<UnbindOperation>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, UnbindOperation, Operation

    public abstract class UnbindOperationWrapper
extends OperationWrapper<UnbindOperation>
implements UnbindOperation
    This abstract class wraps/decorates a given unbind operation. This class will be extended by sub-classes to enhance the functionality of the UnbindOperationBasis.
